      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON COPY (8) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 23.15 beating MIRACLE MAN. Outside box to overcome but goes well over this trip. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Expected to measure up again. FANTASTIC ADA (2) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from six starts. Comes off a (23.30) win last time, scoring by 3.5 lengths in a Other over 400m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. MAGIC NANCY (4) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 10 lengths fifth (24.00) last time in a Other at this track over 400m. Key player if finds best. MIRACLE MAN (6) collected a minor prize last start over this track and distance - must be considered.",
